list.abstract: 《Privacy》是韩国女子组合Rainbow第三张迷你专辑《Innocent》中的收录曲，专辑发行于2015年2月23日。 通过神秘梦幻的感觉将成员们视觉感官及强烈的编舞扩到最大化，成员的靓丽外形和热舞都十分抢眼，突破以往明朗健康的形象，展现出更多高雅迷人的魅力。
《Privacy》是Michael Jackson、Slash演唱的一首歌曲，由Michael Jackson、Rodney Jerkins作词并作曲，收录于迈克尔·约瑟夫·杰克逊于2001年10月30日发行的专辑《Invincible》。

yingyinNormal.en: Mom's trying to guess Haley's iCloud password, which, personally, I think is an invasion of her privacy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈妈在猜海莉的iCloud密码，个人觉得这侵犯了她的隐私。

yingyinNormal.en: And we ask just for the sake of my mother's dignity and well-being that you respect her privacy. Thank you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看在我母亲尊严和健康的分上，我们请求大家尊重她的隐私，谢谢。

yingyinNormal.en: I call these circles Zones of Privacy. Don't Google that unless you want to see picutures of people's genitals.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我管这些圆圈叫“隐私地带”。别搜索这个词，除非你想看人类性器官的图片。

yingyinNormal.en: I won't take your time, gentlemen. This is only to say that my staff and I are committed to protecting your privacy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不会占用两位先生太多时间，我来这就是想跟你们说明，我和酒店员工绝对会保护你们的隐私。

yingyinNormal.en: No, no. Listen, Ross is too nice to say anything, but this is his apartment, and, we gotta have some boundaries, so why don't you go back to your place and give us some privacy?
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，罗斯太好心了，没办法说出口，但这是他的公寓，我们需要隐私，你为什么不回你家呢？

yingyinNormal.en: And I suppose in the beginning we were strangers, who didn't know much about the other and sometimes we did compete for the shower and there were times when we did intrude on each other's privacy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想在最初我们是陌生人，不认识对方，有时还抢洗澡的时间，也有侵犯对方隐私的时候。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm very happy to report that I've just come back from federal court, where my legal team won a major victory for Chumhum against these intrusions on all of our privacy rights by the NSA!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很高兴地告诉大家，我刚从联邦法院回来，我的律师团为查查网取得 了重大的胜利，粉碎了国家安全局对我们隐私权的侵犯。

yingyinNormal.en: Hello. Hey, buddy, can we have some privacy?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们在呀。伙计，你能回避一下吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I think we should give Corrigan our suite on the way back, give him some privacy from the press.
yingyinNormal.zh: 回程的时候应该把我们的套间给科里根住，别让媒体去打扰他。

yingyinNormal.en: Actually, can we do it in private? All right. Go away. I agree, it's rude, but she asked for privacy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们能私下谈吗？好吧，走开。我知道很无礼，但她要私下谈。

yingyinNormal.en: My workout is the only time of day the press corps gives me some privacy. How did your event go tonight?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我只有健身的时候记者团才不来打扰。今晚的活动怎么样？

yingyinNormal.en: Say, I opened this earlier, but let me give you guys some privacy. No nonsense. We're all in this together.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我得给你们私人空间。没关系，我们可以一起。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I'm at a spa, might as well do something relaxing. Sheldon, why don't we give them some privacy? Very well.
yingyinNormal.zh: 反正我在水疗度假村，不妨做一些放松的事。谢尔顿，让他们单独聊聊。好的。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: the condition of being concealed or hidden

examination_example.sentence: But <highlight>privacy</highlight> is not the only angle in this case and not even the most important.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是隐私问题并不是此案例涉及的唯一问题，甚至也算不上是最重要的问题。

examination_example.sentence: Americans should take steps to protect their digital <highlight>privacy</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国人应该采取措施保护他们的数据隐私。

examination_example.sentence: There are concerns that government, employers, and marketers might be able to access these data, thereby violating our <highlight>privacy</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 人们担心政府、雇主和营销人员可能会访问这些数据，从而侵犯我们的隐私。

word_usage.usage:
privacy为不可数名词，没有复数形式，in the privacy of sth. 表示“独自呆在……” ，如：
She longed to be in the privacy of her own room.
她渴望呆在自己的房间，没有人干扰。。
